      {
         "id": "SECTION_first_idea",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Um primeiro passo\n\nPara melhor entendermos nossas necessidades, vamos utilizar figuras geométricas que nos auxiliem a compreender melhor o que desejamos fazer. Primeiramente, vamos desenhar um retângulo com o comprimento da reta do **Gráfico 1**.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg width=\"420\" height=\"140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"2\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"110\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"0\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">0</text> <text x=\"40\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">1</text> <text x=\"80\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">2</text> <text x=\"120\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">3</text> <text x=\"160\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">4</text> <text x=\"200\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">5</text> <text x=\"240\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">6</text> <text x=\"280\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">7</text> <text x=\"320\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">8</text> <text x=\"360\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"1.5em\">9</text> <line x1=\"5\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"5\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"45\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"125\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"125\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"205\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"245\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"245\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"285\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"285\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"325\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"325\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"365\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"365\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" />  <rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"365\" height=\"95\" fill=\"lightblue\" stroke-width=\"0\"/> </svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 2</b>: Representação de um retângulo sobre um caminho.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "O retângulo sobre os números não resolve nosso problema inicial, mas pode nos conduzir a conclusões que o resolvam.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflexão 2: Preenchendo ...</b><br /><br />Olhando para o <b>Gráfico 2</b>, como você utilizaria um retângulo (ou retângulos) para resolver nosso problema de espaços?</div></div></center>",
               "source": null,
